data.description:
Beautifully updated multilevel home. This home offers 3 bed and 3 full baths, updated farm house kitchen. Large entertaining decks off main level .All baths have been beautifully updated, new laminate wood flooring through out main level and lower level family room. Laundry is upstairs close to all bedrooms for convenience . Lower level has a wet bar in the large family room with a fireplace. master bedroom has 2 large closets along with access to a sitting area deck.Attached 2 car garage. back yard is fully fenced with a large shed and raised garden beds Close to Evans Rec. Center & swimming pool, parks &.Schools

Please remove shoes is bad weather. No overlapping showings at this time. Listing agent is a CTM user
